=== 羅馬尼亞 ===
2020年11月26日，[[羅馬尼亞|羅馬尼亞]]的[[皮亞特拉-尼亞姆茨|皮亞特拉-尼亞姆茨]]城市的Bâtca Doamnei山丘上發現了一個與在猶他州幾乎相同的巨碑，靠近歷史悠久的Petrodava Dacian堡壘。這個巨碑是在私人地方被發現，據說是「非法」放置的。目前此事件正在調查中。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.ladbible.com/news/news-mysterious-monolith-similar-to-one-found-in-utah-appears-in-romania-20201130 |title = Mysterious Monolith Similar To One Found In Utah Appears On Romanian Hillside |author = Jess Hardiman |date = 2020-11-30 |publisher = LADbible |language = en |access-date = 2020-12-01 |archive-date = 2020-11-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201130142604/https://www.ladbible.com/news/news-mysterious-monolith-similar-to-one-found-in-utah-appears-in-romania-20201130 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

{{link-en|Jurnal FM|Jurnal FM}}表示，他們實際上在前一個星期二，特別是在猶他州巨碑消失之前「收到一封郵件，內容是有關於在一座山丘上發現的一個奇怪結構物的片段和一些照片」。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://jurnalfm.ro/2020/11/27/mysterious-monolith-discovered-in-piatra-neamt-romania/ |title = Mysterious monolith discovered in Piatra Neamț - Romania |publisher = Jurnal FM |language = en |access-date = 2020-12-01 |archive-date = 2020-11-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201128130810/https://jurnalfm.ro/2020/11/27/mysterious-monolith-discovered-in-piatra-neamt-romania/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>片段指出了該結構物與猶他州巨碑的相似之處，同時也強調了其反射性和紋理的重大差異。11月29日，Jurnal FM發布最新消息稱，來自羅馬尼亞的巨碑也消失了，並提到有人報告說有一束「亮光」，不過沒有提供該報告的具體來源。「當地人以為光線來自一輛汽車，但光線是射向天空的。在早上，巨碑豎立的地方已經空了，只有被積雪覆蓋的地面上殘留著一個淡淡的印記。」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://jurnalfm.ro/2020/11/30/monolith-disappeared/ |title = Monolith Disappeared.. |publisher = Jurnal FM |language = en |access-date = 2020-12-01 |archive-date = 2020-11-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201130144831/https://jurnalfm.ro/2020/11/30/monolith-disappeared/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

12月1日，當地的一家報紙《Ziar Piatra Neamț》向[[路透社|路透社]]證實，羅馬尼亞的巨碑已經消失。該報還稱，「顯然」是由一名「差勁的當地焊工」製作，但此人的身份仍然不明。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cnet.com/news/another-mysterious-monolith-disappeared-in-romania/ |title = Another mysterious monolith has disappeared, in Romania |author = Abrar Al-Heeti |date = 2020-12-01 |publisher = CNET |language = en |access-date = 2020-12-03 |archive-date = 2020-12-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201201201050/https://www.cnet.com/news/another-mysterious-monolith-disappeared-in-romania/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 加利福尼亞州 ===
12月2日，在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[阿塔斯卡德羅_(加利福尼亞州)|阿塔斯卡德羅]]的松樹山（Pine Mountain）發現了一個三角形的反光金屬柱子。它似乎是空心的，没有固定在地面上。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://atascaderonews.com/news/mystery-obelisk-appears-on-pine-mountain/ |title = Mystery Obelisk Appears on Pine Mountain |date = 2020-12-02 |publisher = Atascadero News |language = en |access-date = 2020-12-03 |archive-date = 2021-01-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210103130717/https://atascaderonews.com/news/mystery-obelisk-appears-on-pine-mountain/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>12月4日，三名來自橙縣（Orange County）的青年在{{link-en|DLive|DLive}}上直播自己摧毀巨碑的過程，用大型的木造十字架取代它，並高呼「基督是王！」（Christ is king!），這些青年似乎認為巨碑是反基督，鼓吹[[非法移民|非法移民]]，並與[[反法西斯主義運動_(美國)|反法西斯主義運動]]有關。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.mic.com/p/a-third-mysterious-monolith-has-been-torn-down-by-racists-chanting-christ-is-king-47813409 |title = A third mysterious monolith has been torn down by racists chanting "Christ is king" |author = Tebany Yune |date = 2020-12-04 |publisher = Mic |language = en |access-date = 2020-12-04 |archive-date = 2021-01-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210121175810/https://www.mic.com/p/a-third-mysterious-monolith-has-been-torn-down-by-racists-chanting-christ-is-king-47813409 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 荷蘭 ===
2020年12月6日，[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[菲士蘭省|菲士蘭省]]的{{link-en|Oudehorne|Oudehorne}}中的一個自然保護區發現一個三角形的銀色巨碑。目前不知道是誰擺放這個巨碑。

=== 英國 ===
2020年12月6日，在[[懷特島郡|懷特島郡]]的康普頓海灘（Compton Beach）發現一個與猶他州結構物幾乎相同的反光巨碑。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.sky.com/story/monolith-discovered-on-isle-of-wight-similar-to-ones-found-in-us-and-romania-12153495 |title = Monolith discovered on Isle of Wight similar to ones found in US and Romania |author = Lara Keay |date = 2020-12-07 |publisher = Sky News |language = en |access-date = 2020-12-07 |archive-date = 2020-12-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201206195805/https://news.sky.com/story/monolith-discovered-on-isle-of-wight-similar-to-ones-found-in-us-and-romania-12153495 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

